description: Police arrest a man in Sarpsborg, south-east of the capital Oslo, after three women were attacked.
title: Norway stabbings: Woman killed and two more injured in Sarpsborg
title_page: Norway stabbings: Woman killed and two more injured in Sarpsborg - BBC News
maintext: Another was stabbed in her own home. "We were sitting watching TV and there was a knock at the door. When I opened it he tried to stab me, but I got away," her husband told local newspaper Sarpsborg Arbeiderblad. His wife was then stabbed in the arm.
